00:03:29.815 --> 00:03:30.690
RESHMA SAUJANI: Yeah.

00:03:30.690 --> 00:03:33.240
So Carol Dweck has
this amazing line

00:03:33.240 --> 00:03:36.030
that like, if life were
one long grade school,

00:03:36.030 --> 00:03:38.370
we would rule the world.

00:03:38.370 --> 00:03:40.110
