00:17:19.310 --> 00:17:21.130
And then it's something we
talk about a lot in leadership

00:17:21.130 --> 00:17:21.895
at Google.

00:17:21.895 --> 00:17:23.020
Let's say they get the job.

00:17:23.020 --> 00:17:23.680
And they show up.

00:17:23.680 --> 00:17:25.263
What is the experience
when they show?

00:17:25.263 --> 00:17:27.550
Again, they're fighting
existing structures every step

00:17:27.550 --> 00:17:28.050
of the way.

00:17:28.050 --> 00:17:30.040
So I think once you nail
your current mission,

00:17:30.040 --> 00:17:34.540
I think there's this teaching
Google and our kin, our peers,

00:17:34.540 --> 00:17:37.090
how to hire and
support these women

00:17:37.090 --> 00:17:38.340
when they've landed at Google.

00:17:38.340 --> 00:17:40.048
RESHMA SAUJANI: Yeah,
