00:17:58.243 --> 00:17:59.260
You know what I mean?

00:17:59.260 --> 00:18:01.435
That's what we do, right?

00:18:01.435 --> 00:18:02.060
Let us do that.

00:18:02.060 --> 00:18:03.190
[LAUGHTER]

00:18:03.190 --> 00:18:04.970
Let's build
sisterhood about this.

00:18:04.970 --> 00:18:08.470
And so I think there's
certain basic things that we

00:18:08.470 --> 00:18:10.510
would think are obvious by now.

00:18:10.510 --> 00:18:12.340
And it's a real question.

00:18:12.340 --> 00:18:18.490
Look, a lot of these companies
have been built without us.

00:18:18.490 --> 00:18:21.350
And so they're used to
operating in a certain way.

00:18:21.350 --> 00:18:24.860
And so while the change
is coming, when we come,

00:18:24.860 --> 00:18:27.170
are you ready to change?

00:18:27.170 --> 00:18:29.120
It's a real question.

00:18:29.120 --> 00:18:30.590
And it can't be
something you feel

00:18:30.590 --> 00:18:34.590
like you have to do because
people are telling you to do.

00:18:34.590 --> 00:18:36.980
You have to do it because
you really want to do it.

00:18:36.980 --> 00:18:39.010
You've got to really want us.

00:18:39.010 --> 00:18:40.880
I don't feel comfortable
telling my girls

00:18:40.880 --> 00:18:43.370
